OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a dry day with
OL,6,Fvariable amounts of cloud and sunny
OL,7,Fspells. Some lengthy spells of
OL,8,Fsunshine possible across Shetland by
OL,9,Fafternoon. Light mainly north or north-
OL,10,Feasterly winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,13,Fsome late sunshine. Then it will be
OL,14,Fdry and clear with light winds. A
OL,15,Fchilly night with a slight frost in
OL,16,Fplaces.
OL,17,
OL,18,CThursday:FIt will be dry throughout
OL,19,Fthe day with lengthy spells of
OL,20,Fsunshine. Light and variable winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
